Articles.Content:
So basically I had a fresh install of KSP, installed some mods including EVE. I removed eve to try astronomer's visual packs but turned out not to work, so I decided to just stick with EVE so I re-installed EVE and look up only to see a green sky.

![J13xbx2.jpg](http://i.imgur.com/J13xbx2.jpg)

mods installed with CKAN:

ATM x86 basic

adjustable landing gear

b9

b9 procedural parts

Bahamuto animation module

crossfeed enabler

DDS loader

EVE

EVE - high resolution config

FAR

firespitter plugin

KAE - KSPIextensions

Kerbal alarm clock

KJR

Kinetech animation library

Klockheed martian gimbal

KW rocketry

mechjeb

module manager (latest)

modulercsfx

pilot assistance

raster prop monitor 

RPM core

realchute

resource gen module

smokescreen fx plugin

toolbar

trajectories

tweakscale

vertical velocity control

verginkalactic nodetoggle
